00:46:21.000 --> 00:46:23.448
Just a sec. That's right. Okay.

533
00:46:23.551 --> 00:46:24.931
Now. take the weight of it.

534
00:46:29.724 --> 00:46:31.068
Shit!

535
00:46:33.758 --> 00:46:35.458
They've been bloody clear
about where it was to drill.

536
00:46:35.482 --> 00:46:37.068
Now you've botched it right up.

537
00:46:37.724 --> 00:46:38.724
Okay.

538
00:46:38.793 --> 00:46:40.433
Get some multipurpose
from the van. right?

539
00:46:40.482 --> 00:46:41.896
What the fuck have you...

540
00:46:42.000 --> 00:46:45.068
- Now...
- God.

541
00:46:46.206 --> 00:46:47.424
Now look. it's not that bad. all right?

542
00:46:47.448 --> 00:46:50.241
I did say the tomb may well be empty.

543
00:46:50.344 --> 00:46:53.896
But I was very clear.
it must not be disturbed.

544
00:46:54.517 --> 00:46:56.413
It is sacrosanct.

545
00:46:56.517 --> 00:46:58.758
Please. could you just... just step away?

546
00:46:59.724 --> 00:47:00.758
What's up. mate?

547
00:47:00.862 --> 00:47:02.827
What is it? You all right?

548
00:47:03.068 --> 00:47:04.103
Give it here.

549
00:47:09.068 --> 00:47:10.482
Christ. that stinks.

550
00:47:10.586 --> 00:47:11.586
Well?

551
00:47:14.689 --> 00:47:15.689
What's in there. Bo?

552
00:47:16.896 --> 00:47:17.896
Shaun?

553
00:47:21.586 --> 00:47:22.986
Please. could you just let me look?

554
00:47:37.241 --> 00:47:38.241
Can you swim?

555
00:47:42.482 --> 00:47:43.482
It can be fun. you know?

556
00:47:44.862 --> 00:47:46.068
I need this gone.

557
00:47:46.172 --> 00:47:47.251
<i>I need all of this to stop.</i>

558
00:47:47.275 --> 00:47:48.941
<i>Cos at the moment.
this just feels endless.</i>

559
00:47:48.965 --> 00:47:50.862
It is death after death after death.

560
00:47:51.448 --> 00:47:52.517
Victoria!

561
00:47:53.275 --> 00:47:54.896
- No!
- We believe you are

562
00:47:55.000 --> 00:47:56.000
in imminent danger.

563
00:48:05.413 --> 00:48:06.453
Thank you for the session.
